title: Shares of several energy companies are trading higher despite slight weakness in oil. Oil has been on watch as investors await clarity on OPEC+ output cut plans.

Shares of several energy companies are trading higher in sympathy with the overall market as equities rally on coronavirus vaccine hopes as well as a pickup in economic activity as some US states reopen businesses.
